{"id":39494,"date":"2014-07-07T05:14:03","date_gmt":"2014-07-07T09:14:03","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/staging.budgetsaresexy.vercel.app\/?p=39494"},"modified":"2017-01-12T12:57:53","modified_gmt":"2017-01-12T17:57:53","slug":"anyone-can-buy-that","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/budgetsaresexy.vercel.app\/anyone-can-buy-that\/","title":{"rendered":"Anyone Can Buy That"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>For years I&#8217;ve lived with a maxim that brings a smile to my face every time I repeat it to myself. Which is approximately 38 times a day. I&#8217;ve kept it in long enough, however, and today I release it to the masses.<\/p>\n<p><strong>It&#8217;s called <em>&#8220;Anyone can buy that&#8221;,<\/em> and you remind yourself of it anytime you come across the following situations:<\/strong><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>When you roll up behind a Land Rover\/Benz\/Bimmer<\/li>\n<li>When you walk past a mansion\/mcmansion\/megamansion<\/li>\n<li>When your colleague rocks anything Coach.<\/li>\n<li>When you&#8217;re actuall<i>y sitting<\/i> in coach staring at first!<\/li>\n<li>When your friends are glued to their 82&#8243; plasmas<\/li>\n<li>When you overhear how awesome that $100 bottle of wine tasted<\/li>\n<li><del>When you see someone spending less than they earn<span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><br \/>\n<\/span><\/del><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>It doesn&#8217;t matter if they can afford it or not, or if they paid with cash or credit &#8211; the takeaway is still the same: <em>anyone<\/em> can buy that.<\/p>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https:\/\/budgetsaresexy.vercel.app\/2014\/06\/how-to-save-money\/\" target=\"_blank\">Anyone can save too<\/a>, but unfortunately that&#8217;s harder to see on any given day.<\/strong><\/p>\n<p>So anytime you catch yourself being jealous or salivating over someone else&#8217;s awesome things &#8211; which, let&#8217;s face it, there&#8217;s a lot in life that IS! &#8211; just remind yourself that you can purchase whatever <em>you want<\/em> too. You&#8217;ll probably have to take on some debt or freeze a handful of your goals in return, but you&#8217;re free to pull the trigger any damn time you please. And that&#8217;s quite the liberating feeling.<\/p>\n<p>But remember, every time you don&#8217;t, you get that much closer to freedom. Freedom from stuff, freedom from your job, and freedom to do whatever the hell you want with your life.<\/p>\n<p><strong>Things are nice, but <em>power<\/em> is better.<\/strong> And that&#8217;s something that no one can buy.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-39252\" src=\"https:\/\/budgetsaresexy.vercel.app\/images\/deal-with-it.gif\" alt=\"deal with it\" width=\"384\" height=\"216\" \/><\/p>\n<p>&#8212;&#8212;-<br \/>\n<em>[Fancypants pic by <a href=\"https:\/\/www.flickr.com\/photos\/realburiedtreasure\/2579042436\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">realburiedtreasure<\/a>]<\/em><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>For years I&#8217;ve lived with a maxim that brings a smile to my face every time I repeat it to myself. Which is approximately 38&#8230; <\/p>\n<p class=\"more\"><a class=\"more-link\" href=\"https:\/\/budgetsaresexy.vercel.app\/anyone-can-buy-that\/\">Read More<\/a><\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":3,"featured_media":39496,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[99,98,5,105,12],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-39494","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-awesomely-awesome","category-debt","category-life","category-money-management","category-saving"],"yoast_head":"<!-- This site is optimized with the Yoast SEO Premium plugin v24.6 (Yoast SEO v24.5) - https:\/\/yoast.com\/wordpress\/plugins\/seo\/ -->\n<title>Anyone Can Buy That | Budgets Are Sexy<\/title>\n<meta name=\"robots\" content=\"index, follow, max-snippet:-1,